getAdjustmentFactor

AdjustmentFactor getAdjustmentFactor()
Returns the adjustment factor that was used to adjust this bar prices. Prices of Futures are adjusted based on maturity rolls, Stocks can be adjusted based on corporate actions (splits, dividends...).

nonAdjusted

Bar nonAdjusted()
Returns a new bar with non-adjusted prices. Prices of Futures are adjusted based on maturity rolls, Stocks can be adjusted based on corporate actions (splits, dividends...).
